(text "NOTE: no wires used - connectivity is via matching label names (valid KiCad practice)." (at 20.32 340.36 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7fa14c17-0993-47b5-9a18-3f33bad9efb9))
(text "EC_GPIOx numbering is a local convenience mapping - see U4 pin_nets for actual STM32 pin/net cross-ref." (at 20.32 345.44 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid be1244cd-7159-4d8a-acc8-063cadf13ab6))
(text "Anti-ghosting diodes for the keyboard matrix live on the separate MX ULP keyboard PCB." (at 20.32 351.79 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 95e364e7-4276-41a4-b1bf-b66c004d823c))
(text "MCU_USB_DP/DM (PA12/PA11, OTG_FS device mode) intentionally distinct from Power sheet's USB_DP1/DM1 (PD sink port)." (at 20.32 358.14 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 1cde63e4-fd70-4be7-97b1-ca405e7681d4))
(text "EC can assert Mu PWRBTN_N/RSTBTN_N as open-drain GPIOs; J16 also allows physical case buttons." (at 20.32 364.49 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid f1801b5c-4fc7-4746-ba48-bc20a3585ce6))
(text "Second spare GPIO bank is assigned to E-key radio disables, GNSS UART/control/PPS, OLED reset, trackpad reset/INT, and one spare radio GPIO." (at 20.32 369.57 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7d721a11-50f3-4bd9-9fd0-ef8d8ae4e531))
(text "AUX_DC_ADC monitors the screw-terminal wide-DC input so firmware can classify and current-limit that source." (at 20.32 375.92 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 128036c3-8f7f-4e09-8d4e-dd2df6b613a7))
(text "PA7/PB0 are assigned to skin and Mu-heatsink thermistors; fan PWM/tach remain EC-owned." (at 20.32 383.54 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9cb00ba6-8f28-4ce6-b962-7893d4621509))
(text "J15 is the user-facing EC GPIO header: EC I2C, five GPIO/SPI-capable signals, power, and grounds." (at 20.32 391.16 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 730123ef-c5e8-4bd9-acc0-891e39de703c))
(text "U5 uses TPS54202/TPS54302-style 0.596V feedback; R35/R36 set MCU_3V3 to about 3.30V." (at 20.32 398.78 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid f0454d4a-4df3-4c2b-a136-448d6cd3a494))
